cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper deals with machine learning and computer vision techniques for domain adaptation, which are typically covered in the sub-categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper proposes a novel multi-task learning-based method for unsupervised domain adaptation, which is a popular research area in these sub-categories. Therefore, these five sub-categories are the most likely ones for this paper.
